.IP "Class:	\fBSelectForeground\fR" 4
.IX Item "Class: SelectForeground"
.IP "Switch:	\fB\-selectforeground\fR" 4
.IX Item "Switch: -selectforeground"
.PD
Specifies the foreground color for the selected list entries.
